Package vhacd4

Class Vhacd4Parameters

java.lang.Object
com.jme3.bullet.NativePhysicsObject
vhacd4.Vhacd4Parameters
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Comparable<NativePhysicsObject>
public class Vhacd4Parameters extends NativePhysicsObject implements Cloneable
A set of tuning parameters for convex decomposition, based on version 4 of V-HACD's IVHACD::Parameters.
